## iCloud Sync (Optional)

### What is iCloud Sync?

FishON! Lite offers **optional** iCloud synchronization to sync your preferences across your devices (iPhone, iPad, etc.).

### How iCloud Sync Works

When you enable iCloud Sync:

- ✅ Your selections and preferences sync through **your personal iCloud account**
- ✅ Data is **end-to-end encrypted** by Apple
- ✅ Only **you** can access this data across your devices
- ✅ We (the app developers) **cannot see or access** your iCloud data
- ✅ You can **disable sync at any time** from Settings

### What Syncs via iCloud

- Selected river gauges
- Selected tide stations  
- Custom nicknames
- Flow range preferences
- Custom coordinates

### What Does NOT Sync

- Your purchase history (managed by Apple's StoreKit)
- App settings unrelated to content

**Important:** iCloud Sync is **completely optional**. The app works perfectly without it. All your data stays local on your device if you don't enable sync.

