## In-App Purchases

### How Purchases Work

FishON! Lite offers regional map packs as in-app purchases. These purchases are processed through **Apple's App Store**.

### What Apple Collects

When you make a purchase:
- Apple handles **all** payment processing
- Apple stores your purchase history
- We receive only a confirmation that you purchased a specific pack
- We **never see** your payment information, credit card details, or billing address

### Purchase Data Storage

- Your purchase history is stored by **Apple**, not us
- We store a simple list of which pack IDs you own **locally on your device**
- You can restore purchases on new devices through Apple's system

**Privacy Note:** We have no access to your financial information. All transactions are between you and Apple.

