## Data Security

### How We Protect Your Data

- ✅ All app data is stored **locally on your device** using Apple's secure storage APIs
- ✅ If you enable iCloud Sync, data is encrypted by Apple
- ✅ We use HTTPS for all API communications with government data sources
- ✅ No data is transmitted to our servers (we don't have any!)

### Your Control

You have complete control over your data:

- **Delete selections**: Remove any river or tide station from your watchlist anytime
- **Reset app**: Delete all app data through iOS Settings → FishON! Lite → Reset
- **Delete app**: Uninstalling the app removes all local data
- **Disable iCloud**: Turn off sync in Settings, your iCloud data is preserved but stops syncing

